##We grow vegetables, we cut hair, we fry fries, we flush the toilet... We know nothing of our power

WECHAT betteryourlife2013

The introduction to better your life focuses on the better you and the better world that comes with it.

Forced to stay at home for forty or so days, let the time seems to go back twenty years, we returned to that everything needs self-reliance era.

No deliveries, no takeout, no Tony, and the easy life of money is over for the moment. But self-reliance has also led many to discover that we know nothing of our own power.

You don't have to go to Tony for a haircut; you can buy a few tens of dollars worth of electric tweezers on Taobao to have fun. For 80 bucks to flush the toilet, you can do it with a little toilet press. Like cool skin, fried dough sticks, steamed bread, and other seemingly complex food, cooking is not as hard as it should be.

We just limited ourselves, and now, the seal is broken.

Is this supposed to be a mudslide? When I saw the video of a homemade egg beater on Weibo, I thought it was funny and interesting, so I decided to make one myself. I was in the mood for dessert, and the groupon didn't work out.

I dug out the drill I had bought for the furniture during the previous home renovation, then cut a mineral water bottle in half, cut the bottom in a saw-tooth shape, and drilled a hole in the cap with a nail, and then you put the nail's tail in the drill and you're good to go.

The drill worked quickly for egg white, but you have to press it gently or it will come out. The only drawback is that the drill is a bit heavy and hands are sore.

During the outbreak of the toilet block at home, in addition to their own hands what can be done.

I bought a traditional toilet plunger first. It didn't work. Internet search is not effective, just go to JD.com search, there are many brands of toilet artifacts, but only this one called Bang Tong in stock, I can receive here, will buy the letter.

Shaped like an old bicycle tire pump, it has a barometer that puts the pressure required to open a toilet straight up.

Suggest that we all get one, with it may be out of work for the toilet master.

Recently, the home kitchen inventory is not much, every day to eat bolt eat to death, just want to change the taste. I saw the Douyin Hair Mung bean sprouts tutorial, just have at home to do.

It's a plastic bottle with no big TUB, and my dad put holes in it because Mung beans stink when they're in the water. I flush it twice a day, morning and night, and leave it there when I'm done. On the fourth day, you're fired before you're done, hiccup.

When I eat, my father also said that should use soy, but now Wuhan bean products are quite scarce, my family only last week there is a group purchase of Tofu, so there is nothing to criticize.

When my father was forty, he liked to have a crew cut. He felt cool and convenient. He felt uncomfortable when his hair grew more than one centimeter. During the outbreak, the barbershop was closed. He had no choice. Fortunately, my mother from Taobao spent dozens of dollars to buy an electric pusher, the kind used by children, Razor head has a cover, push against the scalp will not have uneven height.

That day I watched the process of shaving my head, my father has been praised my mother good workmanship, but also a strong amway I also push a crew cut. Later, when he was out shopping for groceries, the clerk at the supermarket who checked his temperature asked him where he had his hair cut, and he proudly showed it off like a kid getting candy.

I had never studied music theory before, although I always wanted to buy electronic organ, but had no chance to realize. I spent the last two days with a friend learning the arrangement, using GarageBand on ios, and really, I learned it in an hour, not as hard as I thought it would be.

It's got all kinds of instruments, and it's got smart instruments. For example, if I'm making up a new pair of pants for do you want to dance, I can choose multiple tracks, first with drums, then bass, guitar, keyboard. The first four octaves sound good in five minutes. It's so much fun.

Barbecue tools used to be in the home, during the outbreak because of the memory of a barbecue stall in Wuhan taste, plus too greedy, learn it at home in the backyard barbecue.

Cut The meat into large pieces and marinate it with salt for ten minutes. The Stove Burns the charcoal, and when roasting, use scissors to cut off the charred parts. When you see the color of the roast is similar to what you can buy at the stand outside, you can sprinkle it with seasonings.

After the barbecue I sent the photos to the barbecue group, was praised by the barbecue stall owner ha ha.

A while ago, the popular circle of friends to do cool skin, see the strategy, the original cool skin is made of high gluten flour. There are winners and losers in our circle of friends. Recently because of the epidemic at home more free time, do not want to see heavy news, decided to follow the wind do Liangpi, went to the supermarket to buy a bag of high gluten flour.

It's a lot more work than I thought. The biggest accident is washing the remaining gluten, I do not know is too low temperature, or too much water inside, yeast fermentation is not good, hole did not rise.

Although not as good as some cold skin shop, but at this time can eat cold skin at home, there is nothing to complain about?

Making Churros is actually quite troublesome, but also oil, the most important thing is that my family did not bubble baking powder, according to the way the home Churros do.

After the dough is well kneaded out of gas, roll into a cake, and then cut into strips. Then the two long stack, with chopsticks placed in the middle pressure, pick up a twist, you can be fried.

My Mom and I actually fried it while we were watching the video, and I thought it was too much trouble, but my mom was fine. We spent our days at home studying food during the outbreak. How else would we spend our time.

I am a liberal arts student, but men will be more interested in mechanical things, plus electronic products such things, take more will be a natural.

I've taken apart Nokia Lumia phones and computers. The first time I took apart my computer, I tried to clean the dust, but when I put it back, I found that I had a few more screws in my hand. Surprisingly, it didn't affect my computer usage, so I threw away the screws and pretended not to have them.

Later, and then open things, learned to open a layer, drawing a layer of schematic memory.

This time it's a simple screen change for the company computer. Because the computer is mainly card buckle, only four screws, it is bold to open. In fact, because the main company does not pay off, so simply buy Taobao screen for themselves. $300,72% GAMUT IPS screen. 15 minutes. Yeah.

-
As life becomes more convenient, many times we prefer to buy results rather than learn and gain experiences through exploration.

So when people have to solve problems themselves these days, it turns out that a lot of things aren't as hard as they think.

Get to it, get new skills, and maybe even get some extra fun out of it.

Text | Wang Bocan
